OL,3,CHow will Birmingham mark the 1st
OL,4,Canniversary of the death of Ozzy
OL,5,COsbourne?
OL,7,FA number of events will take place
OL,8,Ftoday to mark the 1st anniversary of
OL,9,Fthe death of the rock legend Ozzy
OL,10,FOsbourne.
OL,12,FOsbourne was diagnosed with
OL,13,FParkinson's disease in 2019 and died
OL,14,Fat the age of 76 on Tuesday, July 22nd
OL,15,Flast year, surrounded by his family.
OL,17,FHis death came a few weeks after he
OL,18,Freunited with his Black Sabbath
OL,19,Fbandmates on July 5 to play a farewell
OL,20,Fgig at Villa Park ` a stone's throw
OL,21,Ffrom where the band was formed in 1968.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
