OL,3,CHow will Birmingham mark the 1st
OL,4,Canniversary of the death of Ozzy
OL,5,COsbourne?
OL,7,FThe Black Sabbath front man touched
OL,8,Fthe lives of many people from around,
OL,9,Fwhich could be seen by the many
OL,10,Ftributes that were left for him at the
OL,11,FBlack Sabbath bench and bridge in
OL,12,FBirmingham City Centre.
OL,14,FThe council said they wanted to mark
OL,15,Fthe anniversary of his passing with
OL,16,Fits first 'Ozzy Day'.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
