OL,3,CHow will Birmingham mark the 1st
OL,4,Canniversary of the death of Ozzy
OL,5,COsbourne?
OL,7,FIt will provide a free programme of
OL,8,Flive music, art, short films, and
OL,9,Fspecial performances ` with the
OL,10,Ftributes taking place at different
OL,11,Flocations across the city that were
OL,12,Finfluential to Ozzy's life.
OL,14,FThese will include the Black Sabbath
OL,15,FBench and Bridge, Birmingham Museum &
OL,16,FArt Gallery, Birmingham New Street
OL,17,FStation, Bullring, Selfridges, and
OL,18,FMartineau Place.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
