OL,3,CHow will Birmingham mark the 1st
OL,4,Canniversary of the death of Ozzy
OL,5,COsbourne?
OL,7,FThe council said that Birmingham Music
OL,8,FArchive will be giving fans the
OL,9,Fopportunity to share their stories and
OL,10,Fmemories of Ozzy and his
OL,11,F'extraordinary impact on Birmingham
OL,12,Fand the world'.
OL,14,FHere are the events that will take
OL,15,Fplace on Ozzy Day:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
