OL,3,CHow will Birmingham mark the 1st
OL,4,Canniversary of the death of Ozzy
OL,5,COsbourne?
OL,7,F- Ozzy Osbourne : Working Class Hero
OL,8,Fexhibition including Ozzy's iconic
OL,9,Fthrone at Birmingham Museum & Art
OL,10,FGallery, Chamberlain Square, open from
OL,11,F10am to 5pm and will remains open
OL,12,Funtil September.
OL,14,F- Back To The Beginning photo
OL,15,Fexhibition in Grand Central, above New
OL,16,FStreet Station near Foyles book shop
OL,17,Fto mark a year since the final Black
OL,18,FSabbath gig.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
