CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784825275
OL,3,CHow will Birmingham mark the 1st
OL,4,Canniversary of the death of Ozzy
OL,5,COsbourne?
OL,7,FThe council says whether people are
OL,8,Flaying flowers at the Black Sabbath
OL,9,FBench, enjoying live music in the city
OL,10,Fcentre, sharing memories with fellow
OL,11,Ffans or discovering more about Ozzy's
OL,12,Fremarkable journey from Aston to
OL,13,Finternational icon, fans will unite
OL,14,Ffor a day that celebrates a son of the
OL,15,Fcity whose legacy continues to
OL,16,Fresonate around the world.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
