PN,34707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784825275
OL,3,CHow will Birmingham mark the 1st
OL,4,Canniversary of the death of Ozzy
OL,5,COsbourne?
OL,7,FCabinet Member for Culture, Councillor
OL,8,FDeborah Harries said: "Ozzy Osbourne
OL,9,Fis one of Birmingham's foremost
OL,10,Fcultural figures, and we continue to
OL,11,Fhonour his legacy here in the city,
OL,12,Fwhere his journey began. I am glad to
OL,13,Fsee the city partners coming together
OL,14,Fto celebrate Ozzy's influence on music
OL,15,Fand his pride in his hometown.
OL,26,@pD@WOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
