OL,3,CHow will Birmingham mark the 1st
OL,4,Canniversary of the death of Ozzy
OL,5,COsbourne?
OL,7,F"Black Sabbath's contribution to
OL,8,FBirmingham was recognised when they
OL,9,Fwere awarded Freedom of the City on 30
OL,10,FJune 2025. All of these anniversary
OL,11,Fevents are, an opportunity for
OL,12,Fresidents and visitors to celebrate
OL,13,Fthis legacy, while showcasing the
OL,14,Fcreativity, culture and character that
OL,15,Fmake Birmingham so special."
